==Description== 

Expand all placements downwards in the Tree view.

==Usage== 

# Select object in the [[Tree_view|tree view]].
# Select the {{MenuCommand|OpenSCAD → [[Image:OpenSCAD_ExpandPlacements.svg|16px]] Expand Placements}} option from the menu.

==Notes== 

* This tool resets the placement values of an object, making the current position as 0,0,0.
* This tool works with:
** Boolean objects
** Extruded objects (derived from the Part Workbench)
** Revolved objects (derived from the Part Workbench)


